<style>
  #content {font: inherit;vertical-align: baseline;color: #555;font-size: 14px;line-height: 24px;float: right;position: relative;margin: 0 18px 0 0;border: 1px solid #CCCCCC;padding: 10px;border-radius: 8px;;width: 640px;}
  .top-heading {padding:10px 0 !important;line-height: 50px;}
  #content img {border: 1px solid #ccc;padding: 5px;border-radius: 7px;margin: 6px 0 0 0;}
</style>
<%= render :partial=>"/integrations/instructions_left_menu" %>
<div id="content">
  <h1 class="top-heading">Integrate UsersDelight with your BigCommerce Store</h1>
  <p>Helps Bigcommerce customers to increase conversions using Notification, gain customer insights using Survey and have customer support up and running within few seconds using Feedback.</p>

  <div class="content-section-data">
    <p>If you are not signed up with UsersDelight already, you'll need to do so. Please sign up and create a widget for
      your BigCommerce store first. <a href="/pricing">Select a plan and sign-up</a> now.</p>

    <p>Follow these steps to add UsersDelight integration code to your BigCommerce store:</p>

    <h2>1. Go to store's Design control panel</h2>
    <div class="we-thumbnail-container" align="center">
      <img src="//d3701cc9l7v9a6.cloudfront.net/images/v1/platform/bigcommerce-1.gif" height="200" width="600"/>
      <div class="caption">Login to your store's control panel and click "Design"
        link in header navigation</div>
    </div>

    <h2>2. Browse template files</h2>
    <div class="we-thumbnail-container" align="center">
      <img src="//d3701cc9l7v9a6.cloudfront.net/images/v1/platform/bigcommerce-2.gif" height="200" width="600"/>
      <div class="caption">Go to store design &gt; browse template files</div>
    </div>

    <h2>3. Edit Footer.html file</h2>
    <div class="we-thumbnail-container" align="center">
      <img src="//d3701cc9l7v9a6.cloudfront.net/images/v1/platform/bigcommerce-3.gif" height="200" width="600"/>
      <div class="caption">Left sidebar &gt; files used by this template &gt; Footer.html</div>
    </div>

    <h2>4. Copy-paste UsersDelight integration code into Footer.html and save the file</h2>
    <div class="we-thumbnail-container" align="center">
      <img src='/images/webcode.png'/>
      <div class="caption">Get it from UsersDelight Dashboard &gt; Website Campaigns &gt; Add website </div>
    </div>
    <p>
      That's it! Your BigCommerce store is now UsersDelight ready. You can customize your Feedback options, create
      new Surveys and new Notifications in your UsersDelight Dashboard. No code changes are needed on your store.
    </p>
    Note: SSL support is only available for customers subscribed to the <a href="/pricing">Basic plan</a> or higher.
  </div>
</div>